  "instructions": [
    "preheat grill to 400°F (200°C) and brush with coconut oil",
    "soak 12-15 bamboo skewers in water for at least 30 minutes",
    "thread 2-3 pine nuts onto each skewer, leaving a small space between each nut",
    "in a small bowl, whisk together coconut milk, lemon juice, apple cider vinegar, smoked paprika, and minced garlic",
    "brush the pine nut skewers with the coconut milk mixture and sprinkle with salt",
    "grill the skewers for 4-5 minutes on each side, or until slightly charred and smoky",
    "remove the skewers from the grill and sprinkle with chopped cilantro",
    "serve the satay immediately, garnished with additional cilantro if desired"
  ],
